<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>NVH Repo</title>
<style>
body{
    background:#111;
    color:white;
    font-family:Arial,sans-serif;
    text-align:center;
    padding:30px;
}
.logo{
    width:120px;
    border-radius:20px;
}
.btn{
    display:inline-block;
    background:#00cc66;
    color:white;
    padding:12px 25px;
    border-radius:10px;
    text-decoration:none;
    margin-top:20px;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<img class="logo" src="logo.png" alt="Logo">

<h1>NVH Repo</h1>
<p>Kho ứng dụng và tweak của NVH</p>

